    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/dcce01180d9201f18e50d99629c125ff.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/dcce01180d9201f18e50d99629c125ff.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个阴暗的平行宇宙中，人类的残余在机械霸主和噩梦般的生物之间艰难求生，为日益稀少的食物和能源展开激烈争夺。在这个严酷无情的世界里，一个名叫玛尔塔的小女孩，怀着找到失散家人的渴望，踏上了穿越荒凉景观和闹鬼废墟的艰难旅程。她的每一步都充满危险，盟友与敌人的界限变得模糊，生存成为智慧与意志的考验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/2fb4626eb1d96d6948d2be77f27bd384.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/2fb4626eb1d96d6948d2be77f27bd384.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以生存为核心的叙事：</strong> 探索一个机器人、奇异生物和人类为生存必需资源而争夺的平行宇宙。玛尔塔寻找失散家人的旅程在激烈竞争和不断变化的联盟背景下展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/aa68171c688fb08b526d2574125e26a4.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/aa68171c688fb08b526d2574125e26a4.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>资源管理与策略：</strong> 战略性地管理有限的食物和能源，这对玛尔塔的生存和前进至关重要。做出影响联盟和资源分配的艰难决定，塑造玛尔塔的旅程和她所遇到之人的命运。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/160ff8354282116e6dec1a2f251276a2.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/160ff8354282116e6dec1a2f251276a2.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态阵营关系：</strong> 与机器人、生物和人类阵营结盟或对抗，每个阵营都有独特的目标和理念。通过你的行为和选择影响阵营动态，改变玛尔塔的道路和整体故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/3e3b962776520d62c3373c3d1d7b921b.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/3e3b962776520d62c3373c3d1d7b921b.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>创新的生存机制：</strong> 体验超越传统玩法的生存机制，需要适应多变的环境并进行战略规划以克服挑战。探索多样化的景观，适应其独特挑战，寻找关于玛尔塔家人的线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/6c0865421c6644a8d44d55a1182fa974.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/6c0865421c6644a8d44d55a1182fa974.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>情感深度与探索：</strong> 深入体验玛尔塔在充满视觉冲击和氛围的世界中面对失落、勇气与希望的情感旅程。探索反映居民挣扎与坚韧的多样区域，带来丰富的叙事深度和沉浸式探索体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras/57108dba9efe256202cc770b38f169a0.avif?t=1764956611\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3157920/extras_big/57108dba9efe256202cc770b38f169a0.avif?t=1764956611 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
